description:
The Book of Revelation is the only Bible book that pronounces a special blessing upon those who read" it (see Revelation 1:3). There are seven power-packed blessings in Revelation (Revelation 1:3; 14:13; 16:15; 19:9; 20:6; 22:7 and 22:14). If you memorize each one, they will transform your life, and help prepare you for the return of Jesus Christ! Watch Pastor Steve Wohlberg explains each blessing, and how they apply to your life.
